show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: The King of Hell, Lucifer, made a bet with his brother, the Seraph Gabriel. Lucifer predicted humanity would be corrupted by sin in the new millennium and face destruction, while Gabriel predicted they would thrive. God helped Gabriel win, punishing Lucifer by scattering his soul on Earth. A fragment of Lucifer's soul entered a baby girl born in an orphanage during the millennium. To reclaim his soul, Lucifer left Hell...
